Netizen contribution
On August 9, a netizen discovered that Xiaomi phones could not install or update the latest version of Telegram installation package. Netizens tested the package from the official website and found that the latest version of MIUI system could not be installed. There was no bypass button and it could be installed even when the network was disconnected.
